{"type": "article", "id": 8488, "title": "Moooi 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-15T07:17:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234556eZRSQuqOt2jBJVKh.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自荷兰的设计品牌 Moooi 在这次米兰家具展上带来了一套全新的家具系列，部分出自品牌创始人，荷兰设计师 Marcel Wanders 之手，包括蒙德里安《红黄蓝》配色的 Charles Chair，Power Nap 长椅，Arion 限量版椅子，Statistocrat Floor Lamp 等作品。这是<a href=\"http://www.moooi.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Moooi 的官方主页</a>，可以看到他们更多的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234553qI4fZBVhURtJmdDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523455451cyuWN8E7rXBtMT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234554RNTmyI0Q57ZndfOa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234555SknhRZGs2INcClfM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234555dRbjuGKzIHYpLOUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}